  "relations": [],
  "memories": [
    {
      "id": "daiki-mori-memory-rooftop",
      "character_id": "daiki-mori",
      "summary": "Daiki remembers the protagonist looking up at MAGNET as if entry itself were a test. He likes people who understand that doors open for posture before names.",
      "game_date": "2040-08-05"
    },
    {
      "id": "haruto-nakamura-memory-station",
      "character_id": "haruto-nakamura",
      "summary": "Haruto saw the protagonist pause at Hachiko Station, caught between leaving and stepping deeper into the city. The hesitation looked temporary, not weak.",
      "game_date": "2040-08-05"
    },
    {
      "id": "kaito-sugiyama-memory-screens",
      "character_id": "kaito-sugiyama",
      "summary": "Kaito watched the protagonist read the QFRONT screens too carefully. Most people only see brightness; he noticed someone looking for the rules behind it.",
      "game_date": "2040-08-05"
    },
    {
      "id": "ren-takahashi-memory-crossing",
      "character_id": "ren-takahashi",
      "summary": "Ren noticed the protagonist trying to look calm in front of Shibuya 109. The effort interested him more than confidence would have, because it showed hunger without polish.",
      "game_date": "2040-08-05"
    }
  ],
  "dialogueNodes": [
    {
      "id": "daiki-magnet-cool",
      "speaker": "daiki-mori",
      "text": "慎重なのは悪くない。ただ、東京の夜は待ってくれない。欲しいなら、迷ってる顔ごと連れていく覚悟がいる。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/magnet/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"daiki-mori\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": "dialogue/daiki-magnet-start/voices/daiki-magnet-cool.wav",
      "next_dialogue_id": "daiki-magnet-cool-end"
    },
    {
      "id": "daiki-magnet-cool-end",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "彼は短く手を上げて去った。夜風の中に、まだ誘いの形だけが残っている。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/magnet/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "daiki-magnet-line",
      "speaker": "daiki-mori",
      "text": "上に来たい顔をしてる。問題は、招待されたいのか、自分で入る気なのかだ。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/magnet/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"daiki-mori\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": "dialogue/daiki-magnet-start/voices/daiki-magnet-line.wav",
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "daiki-magnet-start",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "MAGNETの上階から、低い音楽と夜風が降りてくる。黒いジャケットの男が、入れる人間を選ぶみたいに階段の先を見ていた。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/magnet/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "daiki-magnet-line"
    },
    {
      "id": "daiki-magnet-warm",
      "speaker": "daiki-mori",
      "text": "いいね。その目なら入口で止まらない。上は静かじゃないけど、街を見下ろすにはちょうどいい。来る？",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/magnet/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"daiki-mori\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": "dialogue/daiki-magnet-start/voices/daiki-magnet-warm.wav",
      "next_dialogue_id": "daiki-magnet-warm-end"
    },
    {
      "id": "daiki-magnet-warm-end",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "ダイキが振り返るだけで、屋上へ続く空気が少し熱を持った。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/magnet/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "haruto-hachiko-cool",
      "speaker": "haruto-nakamura",
      "text": "帰り道を残すのは大切だ。だが、残しすぎると何も始まらない。今夜の君は、どちらに見られたい？",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/hachiko-station/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"haruto-nakamura\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "haruto-hachiko-cool-end"
    },
    {
      "id": "haruto-hachiko-cool-end",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "彼の問いだけが、改札の光より長く胸に残った。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/hachiko-station/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "haruto-hachiko-line",
      "speaker": "haruto-nakamura",
      "text": "ここで待つ人は多い。けれど、選ばれるまで待つ人と、自分で向かう人は違う。君はどちらかな。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/hachiko-station/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"haruto-nakamura\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "haruto-hachiko-start",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "ハチ公前の人波は、待ち合わせと別れを同じ速度で運んでいた。長い髪を結んだ男が、その流れの中心で静かに立っている。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/hachiko-station/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "haruto-hachiko-line"
    },
    {
      "id": "haruto-hachiko-warm",
      "speaker": "haruto-nakamura",
      "text": "落ち着いていて賢い。急ぐ街ほど、足を止める人間の値打ちが見える。少しだけ、こちらへ。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/hachiko-station/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"haruto-nakamura\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "haruto-hachiko-warm-end"
    },
    {
      "id": "haruto-hachiko-warm-end",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "ハルトの声は低く、駅の騒音の中でも不思議と聞き逃せなかった。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/hachiko-station/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "kaito-qfront-cool",
      "speaker": "kaito-sugiyama",
      "text": "正直でいい。眩しさに酔う前に構造を見る癖をつけなさい。そうすれば、選ばれる側から選ぶ側へ移れる。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/qfront/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"kaito-sugiyama\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "kaito-qfront-cool-end"
    },
    {
      "id": "kaito-qfront-cool-end",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "画面が切り替わるたび、カイトの言葉だけが妙にはっきり残った。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/qfront/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "kaito-qfront-line",
      "speaker": "kaito-sugiyama",
      "text": "この画面を見て、綺麗だと思った？ それとも、誰が金を払っているか気になった？",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/qfront/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"kaito-sugiyama\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "kaito-qfront-start",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "QFRONTの巨大な画面が、交差点の顔色を何度も塗り替える。眼鏡の男がその数字の裏側まで読んでいるように立っていた。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/qfront/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "kaito-qfront-line"
    },
    {
      "id": "kaito-qfront-warm",
      "speaker": "kaito-sugiyama",
      "text": "悪くない観察力だ。派手なものほど、誰に見られたいかを隠せない。君も今夜、その側に立ってみる？",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/qfront/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"kaito-sugiyama\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "kaito-qfront-warm-end"
    },
    {
      "id": "kaito-qfront-warm-end",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "カイトの視線を追うと、広告の光がただの背景ではなく、街の序列表に見えた。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/qfront/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ren-shibuya-109-cool",
      "speaker": "ren-takahashi",
      "text": "強がりなら嫌いじゃない。でも渋谷は、飾りだけの自信をすぐ見抜く。次に会う時まで、少し本物にしておいで。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/shibuya-109/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"ren-takahashi\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "ren-shibuya-109-cool-end"
    },
    {
      "id": "ren-shibuya-109-cool-end",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "レンは薄く笑って人波に戻った。残ったのは、試されたという熱だけだった。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/shibuya-109/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ren-shibuya-109-line",
      "speaker": "ren-takahashi",
      "text": "その顔、まだこの街に慣れていないね。でも逃げる顔でもない。どちらを見せたい？",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"cg\",\"cgAssetKey\":\"cg/ren-overlay-test.png\",\"characterIds\":[\"ren-takahashi\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    },
    {
      "id": "ren-shibuya-109-start",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "109の入口は、夜の光を磨いたみたいに白く浮いていた。黒いコートの男が、人の流れから一歩だけ外れてこちらを見ている。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/shibuya-109/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "ren-shibuya-109-line"
    },
    {
      "id": "ren-shibuya-109-warm",
      "speaker": "ren-takahashi",
      "text": "いい返事だ。ここで背伸びできる人間は、案外少ない。少し歩こう。君の緊張が、街に負ける前に。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/shibuya-109/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[\"ren-takahashi\"]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": "ren-shibuya-109-warm-end"
    },
    {
      "id": "ren-shibuya-109-warm-end",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "レンの歩幅に合わせると、ショーウィンドウの光まで味方についたように見えた。",
      "scene": "{\"mode\":\"dialogue\",\"backgroundAssetKey\":\"locations/shibuya-109/background/main.jpg\",\"characterIds\":[]}",
      "voice_asset_key": null,
      "next_dialogue_id": null
    }
  ],
  "dialogueChoices": [
    {
      "id": "daiki-magnet-choice-warm",
      "dialogue_node_id": "daiki-magnet-line",
      "text": "招待されるより、隣に立って入りたい。",
      "next_dialogue_id": "daiki-magnet-warm",
      "sort_order": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "daiki-magnet-choice-cool",
      "dialogue_node_id": "daiki-magnet-line",
      "text": "まだ上に行く理由を選んでいるところだ。",
      "next_dialogue_id": "daiki-magnet-cool",
      "sort_order": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "haruto-hachiko-choice-warm",
      "dialogue_node_id": "haruto-hachiko-line",
      "text": "待つより、自分で向かうほうを選びたい。",
      "next_dialogue_id": "haruto-hachiko-warm",
      "sort_order": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "haruto-hachiko-choice-cool",
      "dialogue_node_id": "haruto-hachiko-line",
      "text": "今はまだ、帰り道を残しておきたい。",
      "next_dialogue_id": "haruto-hachiko-cool",
      "sort_order": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "kaito-qfront-choice-warm",
      "dialogue_node_id": "kaito-qfront-line",
      "text": "誰に見せるための光なのか、気になる。",
      "next_dialogue_id": "kaito-qfront-warm",
      "sort_order": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "kaito-qfront-choice-cool",
      "dialogue_node_id": "kaito-qfront-line",
      "text": "今はまだ綺麗だと思うだけで精一杯だ。",
      "next_dialogue_id": "kaito-qfront-cool",
      "sort_order": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "ren-shibuya-109-choice-warm",
      "dialogue_node_id": "ren-shibuya-109-line",
      "text": "慣れていない。でも、この街に似合うようになりたい。",
      "next_dialogue_id": "ren-shibuya-109-warm",
      "sort_order": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ren-shibuya-109-choice-cool",
      "dialogue_node_id": "ren-shibuya-109-line",
      "text": "逃げるつもりはない。ただ、簡単に読まれたくない。",
      "next_dialogue_id": "ren-shibuya-109-cool",
      "sort_order": 2
    }
  ],
